function Start()
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actor_MahjoobBegin) then
	
		idMahjoobClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_MahjoobBegin)	
		idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMahjoobClone) then	
			Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idMahjoobClone, "NPC_M_Base_wounded_standing")
			Hydra.QActorWait(idMahjoobClone, 0.5)
		
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_MahjoobPreCP1, idOwner, idMahjoobClone)	
			
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idMahjoobClone, actor_MahjoobWave1Arrived, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idMahjoobClone, actor_MahjoobWave1Arrived)
			Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idMahjoobClone, "NPC_Idle_Crouch_Cower")
	
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_MahjoobSomethingWrong, idOwner, idMahjoobClone)
	
			Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idMahjoobClone, 0, actor_MahjoobWave1Arrived)
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(loc_Mahjoob_Wave1, "Wave0")
end

end
